# A - Perfectly Imperfect Array
## Description
[题目链接](https://codeforces.com/contest/1514/problem/A)
## Solution
只要一个数是非完全平方数答案就是 YES。
## Code
```cpp Perfectly Imperfect Array
void solve(int caseNum) {
    cin >> n;
    bool tag = 0;
    for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {
        int x;
        cin >> x;
        int tmp = sqrt(x);
        if (tmp * tmp != x) tag = 1;
    }
    cout << (tag ? "YES" : "NO") << endl;
}
```

# B - AND 0, Sum Big
## Description
[题目链接](https://codeforces.com/contest/1514/problem/B)
## Solution
要使和最大，只需要满足对于任意 $i∈[1,k]$，有且仅有 $1$ 个数第 $i$ 位为 $0$。对于每一位，我们选择一个数使它在这一位为0，其余数在这一位为 $1$，有 $n$ 种选法，一共 $k$ 位，故答案为 $n^k$。
## Code
```cpp AND 0, Sum Big
#include <bits/stdc++.h>

#define debug(x) cerr << #x << " = " << x << endl

using namespace std;
typedef long long LL;

const int MAXN = 2E5 + 5;
const int MOD = 1E9 + 7;
int n, k;

LL qpow(LL a, LL b, LL MOD) {
    LL ans = 1, base = a;
    while (b) {
        if (b & 1) ans = ans * base % MOD;
        b >>= 1, base = base * base % MOD;
    }
    return ans;
}

void solve(int caseNum) {
    cin >> n >> k;
    cout << qpow(n, k,MOD) << endl;
}

signed main() {
    ios::sync_with_stdio(false), cin.tie(0), cout.tie(0);
    cin >> testCase;
    for (int i = 1; i <= testCase; i++) solve(i);
    return 0;
}
```

