## Solution
$1,2,....,16$ 的最小公倍数是 $720720$，因此先将每个数变为 $720720$，对于 $i+j$ 是偶数的位置，再加上 $a_{i,j}^2$ 即可。
## Code
```cpp Multiples and Power Differences
const int MAXN = 505;
int n, m, a[MAXN][MAXN];

void solve() {
    cin >> n >> m;
    for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++)
        for (int j = 1; j <= m; j++) {
            cin >> a[i][j];
            if ((i + j) % 2 == 0)
                a[i][j] = 720720 + pow(a[i][j], 4);
            else
                a[i][j] = 720720;
        }
    for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {
        for (int j = 1; j <= m; j++) cout << a[i][j] << " ";
        cout << endl;
    }
}
