# A Juggling Letters
## Description
[题目链接](https://codeforces.ml/contest/1397/problem/A)
## Solution
每个字母出现次数需要是 $n$ 的倍数。
## Code
```cpp Juggling Letters
#include <bits/stdc++.h>

using namespace std;

int T, n;
string s;

signed main() {
    ios::sync_with_stdio(false);
    cin >> T;
    while (T--) {
        cin >> n;
        int cnt[26] = {0};
        for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {
            cin >> s;
            for (int j = 0; j < s.size(); j++) cnt[s[j] - 'a']++;
        }
        bool tag = 1;
        for (int i = 0; i < 26; i++)
            if (cnt[i] % n) tag = 0;
        cout << (tag ? "YES\n" : "NO\n");
    }
    return 0;
}
